name: Introducing The CryptoBabyPunks
description: Due to the CryptoBabyPunk response to the first minting of this piece, here is version2 with more Bbpunks included. I am minting this for the CryptoBabyPunks family to celebrate #OBJKT4OBJKT. I am not an artist, but just a little video to show some love to amazing communities in the CryptoBabyPunks, Hic Et Nunc, Diverse NFT Art. There may be a CryptoBabyPunk that needs adopting so head to www.cryptobabypunks.com to join the family.
